[ProMED-mail thanks Joanne Ocampo for providing further information concerning this large outbreak of undiagnosed gastroenteritis in a Norwegian hotel. Since the initial report of this outbreak the number of cases has increased from 170 to 319, with 6 affected patients now hospitalised. The preliminary conclusion that this outbreak of gastroenteritis is a result of norovirus infection now seems less likely since some patients have remained symptomatic for more than a week. The results of diagnostic tests are pending. - Mod.CP

A HealthMap/ProMED-mail map can be accessed at: http://healthmap.org/r/1FEs.]
